<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 09:13:43 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国国防部长称真主党与以色列的冲突并非不可避免</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/us-defense-sec-says-hezbollah-israel-conflict-not-inevitable-2024-07-30/</link><description>美国国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀并不认为以色列和真主党之间的战斗是不可避免的，并表示华盛顿希望看到事情以外交方式解决。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 08:31:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/us-defense-sec-says-hezbollah-israel-conflict-not-inevitable-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>香港、澳门外国旅游团可免签进入海南</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/foreign-tour-groups-hong-kong-macau-can-enter-hainan-without-visa-2024-07-30/</link><description>据官方媒体周二报道，中国国家移民管理局表示，来自香港和澳门的两人或两人以上的外国旅游团可以免签在中国海南省停留最多六天。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 07:19:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/foreign-tour-groups-hong-kong-macau-can-enter-hainan-without-visa-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟秘书长博雷尔向越南提供南海安全支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/eu-wants-upgrade-ties-with-vietnam-foreign-policy-chief-borrell-says-2024-07-30/</link><description>欧盟外交政策负责人何塞普·博雷尔周二表示，欧盟希望保障南海和平，并告诉越南，欧盟可以帮助提高其海上安全和网络安全能力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 06:16:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/eu-wants-upgrade-ties-with-vietnam-foreign-policy-chief-borrell-says-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>梅洛尼为在华经营的意大利公司寻求更好的条件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/meloni-seeks-better-terms-italian-firms-operating-china-2024-07-30/</link><description>意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼(Giorgia Meloni)周二对记者表示，在退出中国“一带一路”计划后，她来到中国是为了加强与世界第二大经济体的合作，甚至改善贸易关系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 06:06:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/meloni-seeks-better-terms-italian-firms-operating-china-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>世界黄金协会表示，在六月季度疲软之后，印度减税以重振黄金需求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-duty-cut-revive-gold-demand-after-weak-june-quarter-world-gold-council-2024-07-30/</link><description>世界黄金协会 (WGC) 表示，印度第二季度的黄金需求同比下降 5%，但由于进口税大幅降低，当地价格出现调整，2024 年下半年的消费量将有所改善周二。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 06:03:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-duty-cut-revive-gold-demand-after-weak-june-quarter-world-gold-council-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>台湾总统警告中国，推动国防自力更生</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-lai-says-chinas-threat-any-individual-country-is-threat-world-2024-07-30/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德周二表示，中国对任何国家的威胁就是对世界的威胁，并补充说台湾将继续努力促进防御性自力更生和外国武器购买。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 05:53:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-lai-says-chinas-threat-any-individual-country-is-threat-world-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>台湾称与中国就渔民死亡问题达成协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-reaches-agreement-with-china-over-fishermens-deaths-2024-07-30/</link><description>经过几个月的谈判，台湾与中国周二就两名中国渔民在海上事件中丧生一事达成协议，此举可能会缓和敏感的台湾海峡的紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 05:51:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-reaches-agreement-with-china-over-fishermens-deaths-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>贸易部长称印度不会重新考虑允许中国投资的问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-not-rethinking-issue-allowing-chinese-investment-trade-minister-says-2024-07-30/</link><description>印度贸易部长皮尤什·戈亚尔周二表示，印度不会重新考虑允许中国投资的问题。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 05:28:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-not-rethinking-issue-allowing-chinese-investment-trade-minister-says-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>意大利总理梅洛尼：中国对俄罗斯战争努力的支持是“巨大摩擦”的根源</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/italys-meloni-chinas-support-russian-war-effort-source-great-friction-2024-07-30/</link><description>意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼周二在对中国进行正式访问时表示，中国对俄罗斯对乌克兰战争的经济支持是“巨大摩擦”的根源。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 05:12:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/italys-meloni-chinas-support-russian-war-effort-source-great-friction-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>副总理：中国的“新生产力”需要政府和市场的共同努力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-new-productive-forces-need-government-market-efforts-vice-premier-2024-07-30/</link><description>官方媒体周二报道称，中国副总理何立峰强调需要一个协调良好的政府和有效的市场来发展国家的“新生产力”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 03:28:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-new-productive-forces-need-government-market-efforts-vice-premier-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>台风余波带来降雨和洪水，中国四人死亡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/four-killed-rains-floods-remnants-weakened-gaemi-lash-south-china-2024-07-30/</link><description>官方媒体周二称，中国南部省份湖南省因台风“盖米”残余降雨量创纪录，暴雨和洪水造成四人死亡，数千人被迫撤离家园。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 03:07:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/four-killed-rains-floods-remnants-weakened-gaemi-lash-south-china-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>马科斯表示，美国与菲律宾的接触有助于对中国做出“敏捷”反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-philippines-engagements-help-with-agile-responses-china-says-marcos-2024-07-30/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周二告诉美国内阁部长安东尼·布林肯和劳埃德·奥斯汀，马尼拉和华盛顿之间需要定期接触，以确保“灵活”应对菲律宾与中国的海上紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 02:19:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-philippines-engagements-help-with-agile-responses-china-says-marcos-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>由于对中国的担忧，油价稳定在六月初以来的最低水平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-slip-china-demand-concerns-waning-middle-east-worries-2024-07-30/</link><description>周二，油价稳定在六月初以来的最低水平附近，因政府承诺采取经济政策措施以及美国原油和产品库存下降的前景，平衡了对中国需求的担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 01:04:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-slip-china-demand-concerns-waning-middle-east-worries-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美联储、日本央行面前的等待游戏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-29/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 21:48:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>体操-日本队在激动人心的决赛中击败中国队夺得男子团体金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/gymnastics-japan-win-mens-team-gold-2024-07-29/</link><description>桥本大树周一在巴黎奥运会体操男子团体决赛中战胜了中国队，从鞍马上摔倒，最终夺得金牌，他将心痛变成了难以想象的喜悦。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 18:14:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/gymnastics-japan-win-mens-team-gold-2024-07-29/</guid></item></channel></rss>